parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the automatic emergency braking system can cause sudden and unexpected stops, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially if there are vehicles behind.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes or stops without any obstacles or vehicles in front
the "BRAKE" warning flashes on the dashboard
the vehicle slows down or comes to a complete stop without any input from the driver
the driver experiences sudden and unexpected jolts or jerks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty forward collision avoidance sensor can cause the automatic emergency braking system to malfunction, leading to unintended stops or failure to stop in emergency situations, which can result in accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The forward collision avoidance sensor falsely detects objects or vehicles
the "BRAKE" warning flashes on the dashboard
the vehicle suddenly brakes or stops without any obstacles or vehicles in front
the driver experiences sudden and unexpected jolts or jerks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety hazards, including sudden loss of speed, loss of control, and failure of essential systems like brakes and steering.
symptoms: Sudden loss of speed
flashing dashboard lights
loud helicopter-like sound
inability to accelerate
and error messages on the display screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Sudden application of brakes
flashing brake warning light
inability to stop the vehicle
and error messages on the display screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the automatic brake system can cause sudden stops, accidents, and injuries, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Sudden application of brakes
flashing brake warning light
and error messages on the display screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lane Assistance and Adaptive Cruise Control Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of lane assistance and adaptive cruise control systems can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Sudden loss of speed
flashing dashboard lights
and error messages on the display screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the display screen and dashboard can cause distractions, confusion, and accidents, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Flashing dashboard lights
gibberish or locked-up display screen
and error messages on the display screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Sudden shattering of the sunroof
falling glass
and potential loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power
inability to accelerate
and error messages on the display screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without warning
often when the driver is attempting to park or slow down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause injuries, distractions, and accidents.
symptoms: The sunroof shatters suddenly without warning
often while driving or parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the rear window can cause injuries, distractions, and accidents.
symptoms: The rear window shatters suddenly without warning
often while parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioner can cause discomfort, distraction, and decreased visibility.
symptoms: The air conditioner blows hot air
even when set to a cold temperature.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the strut tower can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The strut tower comes apart
often without warning
and can cause the vehicle to become unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the trunk can cause injuries, distractions, and accidents.
symptoms: The trunk does not open or close properly
often getting stuck or closing unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TPMS can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to underinflated tires.
symptoms: The TPMS fails to warn of low tire pressure
often after driving for an extended period.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the touch screen can cause distractions, decreased visibility, and accidents.
symptoms: The touch screen goes black
fails to respond
or has connectivity issues with Apple CarPlay.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake system activates unexpectedly
often without warning
and can cause the vehicle to slow or stop suddenly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the headlights can cause decreased visibility, distractions, and accidents.
symptoms: The headlights fail to provide adequate illumination
often causing a band of darkness on the upper part of the windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the hood latch sensor can cause distractions, decreased visibility, and accidents.
symptoms: The hood latch sensor beeps or vibrates unexpectedly
often without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the keyless start system can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle can roll or move unexpectedly when the keyless start system is turned off while not in park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the cabin heating system can cause discomfort, distraction, and decreased visibility.
symptoms: The cabin heating system fails to warm up the cabin while idling.
